Download TIGER shapes for Tribal Tracts

Source: R/tribal_tracts.R
tt_tribal_tracts.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Tribal Tracts

Usage

tt_tribal_tracts(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. 2000 and 2010-2021 are currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

# Wrapped in try due to false positive 304 errors
try({tt_tribal_tracts()})
